snippet.title: Inner-Tube Climber | Free, endless-climber, mobile game | Unique wall bouncing, polished platforming
snippet.description:
* Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=dev.levi.inner_tube_climber
* App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/inner-tube-climber/id1553158659

Inner-Tube Climber is a free endless climber mobile game with fun wall bouncing and polished platforming controls!

"Oh no! The player is stuck inside their inner tube from a tragic accident, which also left them stuck in the bottom of an endless crevasse!"

Open source: https://github.com/SnoringCatGames/inner-tube-climber

Made with the Godot game engine!
